let me do it for you.

301
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:26,200
Thank you.

302
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,720
But I think I'd better do it myself.

303
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:44,160
Why are you standing there so stiff?

304
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:47,920
Uh, I just feel a bit awkward.

305
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,240
If you feel bad...

306
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:52,000
...you can just give me
a head massage later in return.

307
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,360
I don't really dare
touch an elder's head.

308
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:57,600
Kree!

309
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,400
Just kidding, just kidding.

310
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,240
My hair is dry now.

311
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:06,040
Uh, why don't we sit down instead?

312
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,040
I'll give you that head massage.

313
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:08,160
You aren't going to stand?

314
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:10,080
Uh, sitting down is better.

315
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:12,760
You don't have to be
so polite with me.

316
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:19,280
I'm ready.

317
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:31,280
Have you ever given anyone
a head massage before?

318
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:34,960
Uh, never.

319
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,320
I figured.

320
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:39,400
Usually, when giving a head massage,
people don't sit face-to-face like this.

321
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:41,280
Well, I’ve never done this before.

322
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:43,280
And...

323
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:50,160
...I’ve never liked anyone
as much as you, either.

324
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:11,240
Is this your first kiss, Kree?

325
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:28,560
It’s going in, it’s going in!

326
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:31,480
Yours is so hard to poke.

327
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,000
That previous back-alley doctor...

328
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
