with fake silicone for sure.

329
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,200
Sky, if you keep moaning like that...

330
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,680
...anyone passing by
is gonna get the wrong idea.

331
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:41,200
Then what the hell
do you want me to do?

332
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,640
Everything I do just turns out so sexy.

333
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,960
Uh, this sucks.

334
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:49,680
No parents, no wife.

335
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:52,600
And here I am, getting an IV vitamin drip
just to cure my loneliness.

336
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:53,760
You’ve still got it good, you know...

337
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,040
...having me as a friend.

338
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:57,640
Because some people...
don't even have a single friend...

339
00:16:58,480 --> 00:17:00,440
...in their damn life.

340
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:02,600
I generously gave you
the Angel Skin drip package...

341
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,600
...and you still trash-talk me.

342
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,720
Hey, Doctor Yed.

343
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:06,640
Doctor Yep!

344
00:17:07,120 --> 00:17:09,160
What kind of parents name their kid "Yep"?

345
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,840
There are three siblings.

346
00:17:10,840 --> 00:17:12,280
The oldest sister is named Kem (Needle).

347
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:14,040
The youngest brother is named Gauze.

348
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:15,120
The middle child is named Yep.

349
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:17,520
We're a whole family of doctors.

350
00:17:18,080 --> 00:17:19,920
Did your parents
not love you equally or what?

351
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:23,120
Well, it's still better than
having no parents.

352
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,440
This guy is dragging us
into a drama again.

353
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:29,280
Your goal is to find your father, right?

354
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:30,680
Then I'll help you out.

355
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:34,800
Fine, and I'll help you...

356
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:37,680
...find a guy who was born
a snake to be your husband.

357
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,960
Deal.

358
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,200
Tap it gently, will you?

359
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:43,840
Huh?

360
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:44,880
You slapped it so hard, holy shit.

361
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:48,240
Okay, let's try again.

362
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:50,000
And what I need to do is...

363
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,840
stop liking that traitor!

364
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,720
Yeah!

365
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:54,840
Hey, who's that?

366
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:55,800
Huh?

367
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:56,720
Who?

368
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,520
Yeah, who the hell is that?

369
00:17:58,520 --> 00:17:59,520
I'm so high.

370
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:11,880
