Glamorous Airline regulation...

470
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:54,720
...456-8, section 6,
the very last line.

471
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:55,720
Negligence...

472
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:57,280
...which resulted in the crew...

473
00:23:57,280 --> 00:23:58,840
...almost losing their lives.

474
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:01,120
Correct. What else?

475
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:07,800
Um, likely regulation 286-6,
paragraph 6...

476
00:24:07,800 --> 00:24:10,360
...section 9,
"keep your composure".

477
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:13,400
"just a coworker",
"don't catch feelings".

478
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:16,080
Understood.

479
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:18,400
This regulation is a major offense...

480
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:21,120
...and is grounds for termination.

481
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:24,120
Understood.

482
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:26,680
I will handle my own feelings
much better.

483
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:28,680
Once you're back on the aircraft...

484
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:31,760
...go earn back your respect and trust.

485
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:34,680
Petchgam Ploy Ployglamjetz.

486
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,280
Understood.

487
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:45,840
I am Petchgam Ploy.

488
00:24:45,840 --> 00:24:47,000
As the purser...

489
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:49,000
...I would like to officially
apologize to everyone...

490
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:51,320
...for the unexpected
events that occurred.

491
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:53,600
Please accept my apologies.

492
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,440
Actually, Ms. Petch,
you don't have to...

493
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:58,280
...blame yourself like that.

494
00:24:58,280 --> 00:24:59,360
It was an accident.

495
00:24:59,360 --> 00:25:01,200
All of us understand.

496
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:02,680
Ms. Petchgam Ploy...

497
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:04,400
...please stop blaming yourself.

498
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:08,360
Thank you.
Please make yourselves comfortable.

499
00:25:08,360 --> 00:25:11,080
Everyone is very exhausted.

500
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,400
Next up...

501
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,680
...I’d like the opportunity to clarify...

502
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,080
...several matters...

503
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:19,240
that might have caused you
all to misunderstand me.

504
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:21,240
