might have been unfair to Ms. Petchgam Ploy.

507
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:30,000
Holy shit.

508
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,360
And I talked a lot of crap
about Ms. Petchgam Ploy too.

509
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:33,360
Me too.

510
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:35,960
Wow, I'm so lucky.

511
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,880
I’m not really the type
to gossip about people.

512
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:40,280
Oh, shut up.

513
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:42,320
Oh...

514
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:44,800
Play the recorded audio.

515
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,920
She must definitely
have something going on with Kree.

516
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:49,000
She made us work our asses off
looking for food...

517
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:51,160
...just so she could pamper Kree.

518
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:54,680
